1. Narrow the channel into 2–3 repeatable content lanes
Right now the description sounds broad: fish, your fish, beginner advice. That is fine for a start, but broad channels usually grow slower because viewers and YouTube both struggle to know what audience to send them to. Since your channel already signals aquatics + beginner advice, I would lean into:

beginner fish care
